name: how-high-am-i-in-utah

Invocation Name: utah elevation
des:
Ask for your elevation.

Utah Elevation will find your elevation in utah.

To start, just say "Alexa, open Utah Elevation".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
